name: Hard-Boiled Wonderland and the End of the World
description: "'As you can see, nobody comes around here. Nobody, except the dream reader'. I nod slowly, but my eyes don't leave her face. Her eyes, her lips, her uncovered forehead by her black hair tied in the back of her head. The more I look at her, as if I were reading something, the more my general impression of her disappears. Lost, I close my eyes"
